title: #DisneyParksLIVE: Watch Main Street Electrical Parade Live from Disneyland Park at 8:55 p.m. PT
text: In just under an hour, we’ll present our next #DisneyParksLIVE stream here on the Disney Parks Blog – Main Street Electrical Parade live from Disneyland park! Our live stream will begin at 8:55 p.m. PT. As you’re watching, share your favorite Main Street Electrical Parade memories in the comments!
